Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
restore_db_st...sign_in_memory(25.10)    restore_db_st...sign_in_memory(25.10)

Name
       restore_db_stop_at_design_in_memory

Syntax
        restore_db_stop_at_design_in_memory { 0| 1}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: 1

       By  default,  tool gives error and stops if you call restoreDesign more
       than once in the same  Innovus  session  unless  restore_db_stop_at_de-
       sign_in_memory  is  set  to 0. Using restoreDesign twice in one Innovus
       session is not recommended as settings from the first database may  not
       be cleaned up properly and can cause problems in the second database.

